pxe-update (1.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream version 1.2:
  * [fd79eff] Use dpkg --compare-versions to compare release versions
  * [cdf77c8] Check remote release directories instead of netboot directories
  * [8c59a04] Add function names in error messages
  * [5f07087] Add remote dir check in function mirror_remote_dir
  * [584fc20] Fix abort_loop function and calls
  * [9081048] Fix architectures processing
  * [bde1a90] Fix handling of PROCESSED_RELEASES_LIST / PROCESSED_DISTRIBS_LIST
  * [f141cef] Fix EFI boot files linking

  * Packaging changes:
  * [7e8cce8] Add dependency on dpkg (>= 1.2.1)
  * [3d1d6e5] Bump debhelper compatibility level to 12

